<DATE>04/07/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Tom</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I bought this van new for my family needs. I have 27,000 miles on it now and have had no problems so far. The only complaint I have is the transmission downshifting from 2nd gear to 1st gear. It has a very hard downshift that is very noticable. If feels like I'm doing damage by driving it with this condition. I started noticing it around 800 miles and thought maybe it was just breaking itself in. I took it to the dealer and they said that they could find nothing wrong with it. I personally think that they don't want to acknowledge the problem. Other than the transmission, I really like the van.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Price, comfort...</FAVORITE>
</DOC>
