<DATE>03/22/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>mike</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Now have just under 80,000 miles. Van has been excellent. Still have original tires and brakes. Only part replaced was a rear bearing hub. Highway mileage on straight run is 26 mpg, consistent 20 mpg in town. Van has been my first van ever and would easily buy another due to versatility. Have not had the transmission issues mentioned in other posts. I have zero complaints.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Versatility, mileage, dependability</FAVORITE>
